    "basic_qualifications": "- 3+ years of data engineering experience<br/>- Experience with data modeling, warehousing and building ETL pipelines<br/>- Knowledge of distributed systems as it pertains to data storage and computing<br/>- Experience in at least one modern scripting or programming language, such as Python, Java, Scala, or NodeJS",
